        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-09-08 15:56:51.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nNormally we would increment the bootstrap image version number in pom.xml and version.properties when there's a change to a blueprint.   I notice, however, that there's another recently-merged blueprint change (111897) that incremented the bootstrap image version to 2.1.3.  The 2.1.3 image has not been released yet.  If we are careful when we do the release and make sure we point to a snapshot image that includes the tcagen2 blueprint fix, we should be OK.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      }
